    "name": "A la Card",
    "steam_appid": 3180680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/6d0d16ae453634eac81afe26affd6052.poster.avif?t=1769033816\" width=800 height=219 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/6d0d16ae453634eac81afe26affd6052.webm?t=1769033816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A la Card</i> is a <strong>food truck deckbuilding roguelike</strong> where you'll mix and match the best aspects of every card you find to create <strong>absurd synergies </strong>and make new discoveries every time you play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/c9af07393632b3621b2cfbd553995f94.poster.avif?t=1769033816\" width=1170 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/c9af07393632b3621b2cfbd553995f94.webm?t=1769033816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stick the effect of one food onto another</strong>. Change what triggers that effect in the first place. Swap stats, inherit flavours, and <strong>cook up clever combinations no one else will</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/08910b206b6d9424ecd975c94635e506.poster.avif?t=1769033816\" width=750 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/08910b206b6d9424ecd975c94635e506.webm?t=1769033816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is an ebb and flow of cramming as many calories as possible into the window before hittin' the road to slap together the most <strong>powerful cards </strong>you can conceive of. These people want food? <i>Oh you'll give them food.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/e767f309aa1c92c445192a4e0110f715.avif?t=1769033816\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it won't be enough to just make a really big burger. <strong>Zany bosses</strong> bring self-contained puzzles to navigate, testing your deck's flexibility. They'll slip you a card and refuse to leave until you serve it to them or clog the window with half-eaten scrap. <strong>You'd better be able to improvise</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Served with a garnish of <strong>tasty tunes</strong> made to order by Josh Whelchel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/a6b86ca913e4a027abd60ad7e8514539.avif?t=1769033816\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Features:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sequence your cards</strong> to make the most of their effects. Skilled players are rewarded for clever plays.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine the calories of your ingredients using <strong>powerful recipes</strong>, creating space to serve even more food! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random special events</strong> provide opportunities to change each and every detail of your cards: the colours, calories, effects, how you trigger those effects, and more! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each starting deck has a <strong>unique and powerful trinket</strong> that deeply impacts how it plays, and you'll <strong>find more trinkets</strong> to mix and match throughout your runs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Presiding over each location is a <strong>memorable boss with a unique ability</strong>. When big numbers aren't enough, you'll have to get creative! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win runs to <strong>unlock more</strong> starting decks, trinkets, and release even more cards into the pool for future runs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revisit your favourite decks to take on <strong>special challenges</strong> and earn coveted stars!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>hundreds of cards</strong> and <strong>dozens upon dozens of mid-game events and upgrades,</strong> no two runs are ever the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180680/extras/f4198992df802d61d5ac3c64cc36b825.avif?t=1769033816\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
